textBox.richText: Regarding the Topic of Occurring in a More Quicker Fashion

Things need to speed up. Happen faster. I feel like I’m on the right track now; that lots of good things await “right around the corner,” so to speak, but they’re not happening fast enough. Don’t get me wrong, I’m pretty content with everything at the moment, as well as the idea that there’s a great deal of potential for the future. It just has to happen already. But anyway, expect another installment of Kevin Listens To coming up sometime in the near future; because, yes, I can now continue that exciting series seeing as music now correctly posts here!
